outlet.cuisines: Experience the rich, aromatic flavors of Dakhni cuisine straight from Hyderabad’s old city. From slow-cooked mutton keema to tangy mirchi ka salan, every dish is a heritage bite, curated by skilled home chefs to bring authentic Old City magic to your table. Perfect for house parties or family feasts.
